description:
How ignut can today be? We talk about J. Anthony Brown's true nature. Taylor Swift uses her voice to support the Democrats. Derrick Lewis has the best post fight interview of all time. Hurricane Michael threatens the Gulf. Comedy Roulette is here. Pimpin' talks about NFL scores with the crew. Are You Smarter Than Tommy? Fool #1 VS Fool #2. Today in Closing Remarks, Big Dog talks about changing your environment in order to grow plus more.
